#

Balsamic Glazed Salmon with Asparagus

$18.5
450 kcal
Difficulty: 40%

Allergens:

Fish

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh-ProteinPaleo

Tags:

DinnerHealthyQuick

Description

A succulent salmon fillet glazed with a tangy balsamic reduction, served with perfectly roasted asparagus.

Ingredients

  • Salmon fillets: 2 (6 oz)
  • Balsamic vinegar: 1/4 cup
  • Honey: 2 tablespoons
  • Garlic cloves, minced: 2
  • Asparagus, trimmed: 1 bunch
  • Olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black pepper: to taste
